# GUI for Qube-Servo 3 Control System, should have a start/stop (for control loop), a enable/disable, a reset button if config.QUBE_SIMULATION, and a live plot of the state variables(from Logging) if config.DATA_PLOTTING. It should also display state Swingup/stabalize. The gui when closed terminate the program by setting the global stop_event, which the control loop and uart thread should check to exit gracefully. The GUI runs in the main thread. 